<li> Remember the good times and hold them close to your heart.</li>
<li> Please reach out if you need anything – a shoulder to cry on, an ear to listen, or just some company.</li>
<li> Your father's spirit will live on in your memories.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and sending you all my love and support during this hard time.</li>
<li> I'm here for you, whatever you need, anytime.</li>
<li>May your happy memories bring you peace.</li>
<li>Know that I am thinking of you and your family and sending you strength.</li>
